    "_comment": "SnappyMail domain config for mail.${DOMAIN}. Deployed by scripts/steps/86-install-webmail.sh as <data>/domains/mail.${DOMAIN}.json. Points SnappyMail at the LOOPBACK Maddy mailbox (the email subsystem's IMAP/SMTP listeners); the install step substitutes __IMAP_PORT__ / __SMTP_PORT__ from .env. type 0 = plain (loopback only, no TLS — the connection never leaves the host). All public providers (gmail/outlook/...) are removed by the install step so this is the only domain SnappyMail will serve.",
